  
### XrossBoard ver.1.0.0  

Work with  
* Windows XP, Vista, 7  
* Linux    (GTK2 or 3)  
* Mac OS X (Lion~)  
* BSD      (GTK2 or 3)    
  
###About
  Cross Platform BBS Reader  
  
###Build  
```
  $ ./bootstrap  
  $ ./configure  
  $ make  
```  

  See INSTALL file for detail.  
